 />\n凹凸洞呢啲嘢真係要搵返醫生處理比較好</blockquote><br />\n好明白果種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個凹凸洞範圍都幾大<br />\n基本兩邊面脥都有<br />\n絲打你打算搵邊間做?"},{"pid":"d247ef6adcd52988a398dec1107fa7e1e43a709b","tid":242681,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:51:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想打laser但我見啲人打到成塊面爛哂咁 好驚要成半年都要帶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n我份工仲要成日見人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打好嚴重?</blockquote><br />\n唔算好嚴重嘅 最主要係個鼻同鼻嘅兩側 不過女仔貪靚見到其他人白白滑滑自己的凹凸洞化妝都遮唔到就好唔開心 驚比人近距離望我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前有諗過做果酸換膚 但問過做過嘅巴打佢話對凹凸洞方面嘅幫助唔大<br />\n如果真係嚴重嘅話最有效嘅方法真係打laser<br />\n凹凸洞呢啲嘢真係要搵返醫生處理比較好</blockquote><br />\n好明白果種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個凹凸洞範圍都幾大<br />\n基本兩邊面脥都有<br />\n絲打你打算搵邊間做?</blockquote><br />\n我都唔太知 不過都應該係浸會醫院嗰啲掛<br />\n不過我仲係學生冇乜錢 應該有排先會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59748620b98a3a25eaece7cb54f2f9cebc5a6ab0","tid":242681,"uid":94929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:52:25.000Z","msg":"睇嚴重程度，唔算太嚴重就去左皮膚專科到睇，通常打laser，fraxel repair or restore<br />\n好嚴重的睇整容外科，可以會做subcision or chemical peel"},{"pid":"f32b9712369f069e2186e3c1bdc0d49af9d3a58f","tid":242681,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T10:34:59.000Z","msg":"用針清+搵野磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9208036c4f1f8aa125e9a2c9a6d6aaada76b9a0","tid":242681,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想打laser但我見啲人打到成塊面爛哂咁 好驚要成半年都要帶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n我份工仲要成日見人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打好嚴重?</blockquote><br />\n唔算好嚴重嘅 最主要係個鼻同鼻嘅兩側 不過女仔貪靚見到其他人白白滑滑自己的凹凸洞化妝都遮唔到就好唔開心 驚比人近距離望我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前有諗過做果酸換膚 但問過做過嘅巴打佢話對凹凸洞方面嘅幫助唔大<br />\n如果真係嚴重嘅話最有效嘅方法真係打laser<br />\n凹凸洞呢啲嘢真係要搵返醫生處理比較好</blockquote><br />\n好明白果種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個凹凸洞範圍都幾大<br />\n基本兩邊面脥都有<br />\n絲打你打算搵邊間做?</blockquote><br />\n我都唔太知 不過都應該係浸會醫院嗰啲掛<br />\n不過我仲係學生冇乜錢 應該有排先會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢D野真係想趁後生快D搞<br />\n年紀大左想救都救唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b0f606d3459113ef41464369fe13d78b71546d","tid":242681,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T12:41:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇嚴重程度，唔算太嚴重就去左皮膚專科到睇，通常打laser，fraxel repair or restore<br />\n好嚴重的睇整容外科，可以會做subcision or chemical peel</blockquote><br />\n巴打覺得去醫院睇皮膚科先?<br />\n其實我之前生到最勁果陣<br />\n有食過A酸<br />\n但D印同洞就留左係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b1e98c9bdb19696e669014e3f8f4e7aa601dd0","tid":242681,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T12:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇嚴重程度，唔算太嚴重就去左皮膚專科到睇，通常打laser，fraxel repair or restore<br />\n好嚴重的睇整容外科，可以會做subcision or chemical peel</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係嚴重果隻 可能點搞"},{"pid":"f2934b6ae987760b940d3c189f05a429df7d786e","tid":242681,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T12:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用針清+搵野磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有做?"},{"pid":"c582214b60d99b4f6ddf4bdc52303c144f9dcfbd","tid":242681,"uid":16853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T12:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇嚴重程度，唔算太嚴重就去左皮膚專科到睇，通常打laser，fraxel repair or restore<br />\n好嚴重的睇整容外科，可以會做subcision or chemical peel</blockquote><br />\n巴打覺得去醫院睇皮膚科先?<br />\n其實我之前生到最勁果陣<br />\n有食過A酸<br />\n但D印同洞就留左係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都食過a酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同你情況一樣<br />\n但唔想搵返a酸個醫生做療程 有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c73a15606546e2719dc697c99ff2705868eec69","tid":242681,"uid":94929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇嚴重程度，唔算太嚴重就去左皮膚專科到睇，通常打laser，fraxel repair or restore<br />\n好嚴重的睇整容外科，可以會做subcision or chemical peel</blockquote><br />\n巴打覺得去醫院睇皮膚科先?<br />\n其實我之前生到最勁果陣<br />\n有食過A酸<br />\n但D印同洞就留左係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 你第一次睇 佢會評估你程度 唔會轉彎抹角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果好嚴重既ice pick scars就通常做laser改變既程度都不高 你預2 3成"},{"pid":"0758d761964db72227cb470f506084f38db5ff44","tid":242681,"uid":94929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:03:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇嚴重程度，唔算太嚴重就去左皮膚專科到睇，通常打laser，fraxel repair or restore<br />\n好嚴重的睇整容外科，可以會做subcision or chemical peel</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係嚴重果隻 可能點搞</blockquote><br />\n睇整容外科，通常可能會做左chemical peel/subcision 減輕後再用機磨<br />\n同樣地第一次預約醫生做評估"},{"pid":"bebe57bb915a71eed2697bbd238243779955ed87","tid":242681,"uid":7878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中學爆得好勁<br />\n大個左好返d<br />\n除左凹凸洞之外 塊面長期好紅 點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527373ed59c598586a1653a3b114ac81064c6255","tid":242681,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:04:52.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"161cfbb5f6d50ebc09e8e42ae434c476d44764d8","tid":242681,"uid":91173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:15:43.000Z","msg":"印的話可以打LASER同做CHEMICAL PEEL<br />\n凹凸洞就要做D創傷性勁D GE LASER<br />\n如果你要即時效果, 打針都可以, 但唔長遠 會慢慢流失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己係毛孔太大而去做LASER<br />\n打完會結焦起砂咁, 5-7日會甩晒<br />\n每月打一次(治療師話), 我係個零兩個月打一次<br />\n而家都打左8次左右<br />\n過程係有D慢但都見得到有效果<br />\n同埋要keep住做一排先會有用"},{"pid":"0b25139933a7b98c5d189dccfbe0874248d47274","tid":242681,"uid":16853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>印的話可以打LASER同做CHEMICAL PEEL<br />\n凹凸洞就要做D創傷性勁D GE LASER<br />\n如果你要即時效果, 打針都可以, 但唔長遠 會慢慢流失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己係毛孔太大而去做LASER<br />\n打完會結焦起砂咁, 5-7日會甩晒<br />\n每月打一次(治療師話), 我係個零兩個月打一次<br />\n而家都打左8次左右<br />\n過程係有D慢但都見得到有效果<br />\n同埋要keep住做一排先會有用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6480a6f29e906557ff47770abc973664d0b4d4f","tid":242681,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中學爆得好勁<br />\n大個左好返d<br />\n除左凹凸洞之外 塊面長期好紅 點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前都好紅<br />\n後尾啲護膚品轉晒用天然手造野，用一排就退咗好多，同埋訓覺訓多啲<br />\n因為紅嘅原因主要都係敏感，所以盡量用嘅野愈少愈清就愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名睇洞洞點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b2faba093518eb3bf5194895a9f53222364fcd","tid":242681,"uid":51291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"召集更多被暗瘡折磨既巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b221dae43b3bc8e173c3eb907a135e79066db1e1","tid":242681,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:25:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>印的話可以打LASER同做CHEMICAL PEEL<br />\n凹凸洞就要做D創傷性勁D GE LASER<br />\n如果你要即時效果, 打針都可以, 但唔長遠 會慢慢流失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己係毛孔太大而去做LASER<br />\n打完會結焦起砂咁, 5-7日會甩晒<br />\n每月打一次(治療師話), 我係個零兩個月打一次<br />\n而家都打左8次左右<br />\n過程係有D慢但都見得到有效果<br />\n同埋要keep住做一排先會有用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112171dad1486aac3df74a3f8834aab141be4530","tid":242681,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:28:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇嚴重程度，唔算太嚴重就去左皮膚專科到睇，通常打laser，fraxel repair or restore<br />\n好嚴重的睇整容外科，可以會做subcision or chemical peel</blockquote><br />\n巴打覺得去醫院睇皮膚科先?<br />\n其實我之前生到最勁果陣<br />\n有食過A酸<br />\n但D印同洞就留左係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 你第一次睇 佢會評估你程度 唔會轉彎抹角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果好嚴重既ice pick scars就通常做laser改變既程度都不高 你預2 3成</blockquote><br />\n我係網上搵到張圖<br />\n同我個case差唔多<br />\n唔知咁算唔算嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Ana_Manzoni/publication/47754426/figure/fig1/AS:277049638965253@1443065189918/Figure-1-Ice-pick-and-boxcar-type-scars-in-the-malar-regions-before-treatment.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fprofile%2FAna_Manzoni%2Fpublication%2F47754426%2Ffigure%2Ffig1%2FAS%3A277049638965253%401443065189918%2FFigure-1-Ice-pick-and-boxcar-type-scars-in-the-malar-regions-before-treatment.png&h=0cb45017&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d2e8b2f8a8487f10809762b2df615c452932914","tid":242681,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"印 果酸/杏仁酸/海藻矽針換膚 +美白產品<br />\n洞 海藻矽針/laser， 但如果洞太深嘅冇得救"},{"pid":"722f9ccbc2b744661540f49a209ec1f9502abe57","tid":242681,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>印 果酸/杏仁酸/海藻矽針換膚 +美白產品<br />\n洞 海藻矽針/laser， 但如果洞太深嘅冇得救</blockquote><br />\n上面果種有冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ced76f00acd08a43622eed6b2bbd42551eb583","tid":242681,"uid":91173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>印的話可以打LASER同做CHEMICAL PEEL<br />\n凹凸洞就要做D創傷性勁D GE LASER<br />\n如果你要即時效果, 打針都可以, 但唔長遠 會慢慢流失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己係毛孔太大而去做LASER<br />\n打完會結焦起砂咁, 5-7日會甩晒<br />\n每月打一次(治療師話), 我係個零兩個月打一次<br />\n而家都打左8次左右<br />\n過程係有D慢但都見得到有效果<br />\n同埋要keep住做一排先會有用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帶定頭盔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我有用但唔知其他巴絲有無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nfacx collegx 我見佢而家都有免費試做<br />\n好似包左見醫生 當係聽下可以點樣搞返好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86381d93a40af85aa73ebb4742ac4f435558e0af","tid":242681,"uid":47580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:41:57.000Z","msg":"我係個鼻側邊有凹凸洞 我個人覺得幾嚴重<br />\n唔介意嘅話可唔可以自貼個鼻 幫我睇下有冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ab0c5c55d4d53245c366932b20c4ae7be997b0","tid":242681,"uid":91173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇嚴重程度，唔算太嚴重就去左皮膚專科到睇，通常打laser，fraxel repair or restore<br />\n好嚴重的睇整容外科，可以會做subcision or chemical peel</blockquote><br />\n巴打覺得去醫院睇皮膚科先?<br />\n其實我之前生到最勁果陣<br />\n有食過A酸<br />\n但D印同洞就留左係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 你第一次睇 佢會評估你程度 唔會轉彎抹角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果好嚴重既ice pick scars就通常做laser改變既程度都不高 你預2 3成</blockquote><br />\n我係網上搵到張圖<br />\n同我個case差唔多<br />\n唔知咁算唔算嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Ana_Manzoni/publication/47754426/figure/fig1/AS:277049638965253@1443065189918/Figure-1-Ice-pick-and-boxcar-type-scars-in-the-malar-regions-before-treatment.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fprofile%2FAna_Manzoni%2Fpublication%2F47754426%2Ffigure%2Ffig1%2FAS%3A277049638965253%401443065189918%2FFigure-1-Ice-pick-and-boxcar-type-scars-in-the-malar-regions-before-treatment.png&h=0cb45017&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得唔算好嚴重, 我有朋友嚴重過你"},{"pid":"386ee5f0803ef9ed2de2ced31dec9417852084aa","tid":242681,"uid":27433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:03:16.000Z","msg":"Ice pick scar 要做 Tca Cross, 不過香港好似冇見過有得做， Tca Cross 係用一種酸性液體查係 Ice Pick Scar 上， 之後個洞會平返， 可以上youtube 睇睇"},{"pid":"212824b9a2cb2ccaa564fa5347bd1a993ba8016b","tid":242681,"uid":97709,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:13:27.000Z","msg":"路過一問 咁有冇面霜推介可以消除凹凸洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b618d48c2bfd4eac7852a745d361bbb95707de","tid":242681,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:27:01.000Z","msg":"係咪最好睇醫生先整<br />\n想自己買嘢翻嚟試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf3a7e7db24a6a4b8b5af2410682a09536797a5","tid":242681,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:35:55.000Z","m