"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T01:10:41.000Z","msg":"返工唔得閒<br />\n大家討論住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20e093bbaad3614bd2214a1d3fc8b4368c7bcfe","tid":242681,"uid":30425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T03:34:33.000Z","msg":"大家有啲concept要清一清<br />\n針清危險既地方係在於美容師既手勢好唔好，如果遇到個經驗差手勢唔好既就gg，但本質上，針清係最傳統，最低成本，最快捷既去暗粒方法，不過效果要睇手勢，同埋事後功夫好重要"},{"pid":"3adffecddfaeff74cf190637dee8fe41ece1efd3","tid":242681,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T03:38:04.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n一定要搵皮膚醫生打laser<br />\n美容院完全冇用<br />\n醫生打一次6000到<br />\n但keep到2/3個月"},{"pid":"3bedde7108167e28ab5da2a8af7d91a1ca492a38","tid":242681,"uid":115650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T03:40:08.000Z","msg":"上面張圖對我黎講已經好少事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變到佢咁我已經心意滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495605d353c2db572cc44cad90731f14016f71f2","tid":242681,"uid":23552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:01:36.000Z","msg":"依家仲有冇生暗瘡先"},{"pid":"6aa6d27678c6d77fb2eb17489022b1b5d1d7e359","tid":242681,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:02:58.000Z","msg":"laser有邊間推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c5e9fa4e202f322fad4875f122031b9861f5fb","tid":242681,"uid":54854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:05:25.000Z","msg":"一邊面得5粒 冇理由花幾萬蚊去做<br />\n但唔做又唔睇唔順眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3caa43a144110b617d69b3d66b4c6e36cd1b40c","tid":242681,"uid":84163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:05:27.000Z","msg":"想問下易出油同埋毛孔大 做果酸換膚有無用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif