d":"d5bae946c4bb617a0bf9646f76008431d5e652ed","tid":242681,"uid":26450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:12:31.000Z","msg":"爛面撚留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做過一次scarlet rf<br />\n<br />\n好左少少, 少到唔覺眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做多幾次睇下點"},{"pid":"0078b1f3c2a5e1fd254e16e5124b0577a2308529","tid":242681,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多巴絲都話打laser有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但想知打完之後塊面點處理<br />\n通常要打幾多次就有明顯效果</blockquote><br />\n要睇laser強度。<br />\n好似fraxel repair 強度高 打完會爆曬血 成個星期 唔出得街。一個月到d印先返得7788。<br />\nfraxel restore打完好紅 可能少少血咁。<br />\n弱=要打好多次 強=打少d但風險相對高。<br />\n問皮專醫生最好 佢地有經驗過連登仔啦 最好睇多1 2間比較下 因為都貴。。預幾皮啦"},{"pid":"7238298d53edbb2d1db32a369e9bf5b90c5e3d0d","tid":242681,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>laser有邊間推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n皮專做laser黎黎去去都係得 浸會/中環陳醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nok收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陳醫生會唔會開a 酸個d ? 我諗住遲d 睇</blockquote><br />\n會 但食A酸唔使去皮專啦 就咁普通科都夠"},{"pid":"107ee6ad04181f59edf62bb2c795a17cb4d19398","tid":242681,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多巴絲都話打laser有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但想知打完之後塊面點處理<br />\n通常要打幾多次就有明顯效果</blockquote><br />\n要睇laser強度。<br />\n好似fraxel repair 強度高 打完會爆曬血 成個星期 唔出得街。一個月到d印先返得7788。<br />\nfraxel restore打完好紅 可能少少血咁。<br />\n弱=要打好多次 強=打少d但風險相對高。<br />\n問皮專醫生最好 佢地有經驗過連登仔啦 最好睇多1 2間比較下 因為都貴。。預幾皮啦</blockquote><br />\n就咁睇我會揀弱果種<br />\n太強驚自己受唔到<br />\n始終食過a酸皮膚薄"},{"pid":"7da6905f61f97bc5a475af57a5ca5de883bd015d","tid":242681,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中學爆得好勁<br />\n大個左好返d<br />\n除左凹凸洞之外 塊面長期好紅 點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前都好紅<br />\n後尾啲護膚品轉晒用天然手造野，用一排就退咗好多，同埋訓覺訓多啲<br />\n因為紅嘅原因主要都係敏感，所以盡量用嘅野愈少愈清就愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名睇洞洞點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我想問長期好紅即係點？<br />\n我塊面我照鏡都覺得有少少微紅 我唔知係好似你地所講既紅定係暗瘡紅印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想解決啲紅 而家用緊個洗面我想問點睇係咪天然？ 我每次洗完面都想搽cream 但係我鼻旁成日好似有啲粒粒想發出黎 搞到我呢排都靜係落爽膚水only...<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82385d0e1c993717c343ad5eae98dada966c663f","tid":242681,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"打過好多種激光，名都唔記得了<br />\n浸會都打過restore,6千蚊次，打左3次完全無改善就放棄左"},{"pid":"4b05441977dec38ac791fc6ba5949354ef806d37","tid":242681,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打過好多種激光，名都唔記得了<br />\n浸會都打過restore,6千蚊次，打左3次完全無改善就放棄左</blockquote><br />\n巴打打左3次, 一啲效果都冇?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解同樓上幾位巴講既野差咁多"},{"pid":"7209c9386e3ebc2441cfc3d005da203847fb205d","tid":242681,"uid":23552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家仲有冇生暗瘡先</blockquote><br />\n而家就額頭有時會生，但都感覺控制到</blockquote><br />\n睇中醫調理身體先 加埋要戒口（一定要）<br />\n<br />\n啲印會慢慢退 凹凸洞就真係要睇下美容之類果啲"},{"pid":"8d7b990fb6e7c87956e2d3dbe44154f829ab47f0","tid":242681,"uid":94929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor