ss=\"hkgmoji\" />食緊a酸做唔到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飲下檸檬水得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe82360ff655964f4d9ff9585f6418c39b223cf","tid":242681,"uid":61443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T00:59:56.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<br />\n<br />\n食完A酸年幾<br />\n真係生少左90%暗瘡<br />\n<br />\n塊面都幾多凹凸洞 <br />\n想做激光搞搞佢 <br />\n<br />\n生左十幾年暗瘡<br />\n真係想死<br />\n試過N咁多方法<br />\n最後A酸幫到我"},{"pid":"0fc2ed318a20d65358762abfc6864666052537ad","tid":242681,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T01:01:08.000Z","msg":"聽講馬明同張繼聰都有做激光<br />\n請問佢地係做邊隻 ？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2379c52cdc06ee656280b7e2baee3bcc663b0dc","tid":242681,"uid":38451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T01:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講馬明同張繼聰都有做激光<br />\n請問佢地係做邊隻 ？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗係Fractional CO2 Laser<br />\n呢部機有分打疣同凹凸洞 <br />\n而呢隻頭係for凹凸洞<br />\n我地會叫呢種做打爛臉<br />\n通常打完幾日後會起沙<br />\n做一次係清唔曬畢竟呢d積左咁多年好難一次療程就清哂<br />\n上面大家都講到咁貴<br />\n其實有d地方around$2000已經做到一次架啦<br />\n因為做緊診所有laser機所以有d認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2f538ae6cc3d813f3cca122b0c21c2b25a79d6","tid":242681,"uid":36343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽講馬明同張繼聰都有做激光<br />\n請問佢地係做邊隻 ？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗係Fractional CO2 Laser<br />\n呢部機有分打疣同凹凸洞 <br />\n而呢隻頭係for凹凸洞<br />\n我地會叫呢種做打爛臉<br />\n通常打完幾日後會起沙<br />\n做一次係清唔曬畢竟呢d積左咁多年好難一次療程就清哂<br />\n上面大家都講到咁貴<br />\n其實有d地方around$2000已經做到一次架啦<br />\n因為做緊診所有laser機所以有d認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打見啲人打幾多次先有明顯效果？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a6d6c67fffe306834fce694d897068954987cb","tid":242681,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:36:35.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac428d2644845f73f4ff433d72ec66544fe1f3a","tid":242681,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb06b28f6d41739153ec1dd3249aa5aef17c85db","tid":242681,"uid":38451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:43:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽講馬明同張繼聰都有做激光<br />\n請問佢地係做邊隻 ？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗係Fractional CO2 Laser<br />\n呢部機有分打疣同凹凸洞 <br />\n而呢隻頭係for凹凸洞<br />\n我地會叫呢種做打爛臉<br />\n通常打完幾日後會起沙<br />\n做一次係清唔曬畢竟呢d積左咁多年好難一次療程就清哂<br />\n上面大家都講到咁貴<br />\n其實有d地方around$2000已經做到一次架啦<br />\n因為做緊診所有laser機所以有d認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打見啲人打幾多次先有明顯效果？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實就算問治療師醫生都好難答你<br />\n因為呢d要睇你打完返去<br />\n等佢好返哂先知仲有幾多未清<br />\n呢d好見仁見智<br />\n有人打完已經好返八成但佢仲覺得未夠咪繼續打<br />\n睇你接受程度有幾多啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ae6be7b96d318b93cd59f55b65abfc1b99fbf7","tid":242681,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T06:51:55.000Z","msg":"食極a酸都唔好"},{"pid":"c85b06a8ae42d41525c5acc11be01653af46dbb0","tid":242681,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食極a酸都唔好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食咗幾耐？"},{"pid":"b75b81a9673ac0d43c5994bdb914b09460e8f3a5","tid":242681,"uid":45525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:22:30.000Z","msg":"有冇啲天然產品推介係去印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前買過話去印個啲 反而繼續谷暗瘡<br />\